Germany’s Air Traffic Controllers May Strike, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 
2011-06-16T05:25:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-16/germany-s-air-traffic-controllers-may-strike-handelsblatt-says.html
Germany ’s air traffic controllers
may take strike action after pay talks failed,  Handelsblatt 
reported today, citing union spokesman Matthias Maas.  The strike may start in the next few days or, more
probably, in about four weeks, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporters on this story:
